WEBVTT

00:15:29.720 --> 00:15:32.976
or the split of domestic duties

00:15:33.000 --> 00:15:34.680
or the gender pay gap.

00:15:36.280 --> 00:15:38.056
But I believe that as men,

00:15:38.080 --> 00:15:40.536
it's time we start to see
past our privilege

00:15:40.560 --> 00:15:43.176
and recognize that we are
not just part of the problem.

00:15:43.200 --> 00:15:44.896
Fellas, we are the problem.

00:15:44.920 --> 00:15:48.096
The glass ceiling exists
because we put it there,

00:15:48.120 --> 00:15:50.216
and if we want to be
a part of the solution,

00:15:50.240 --> 00:15:51.800
then words are no longer enough.

00:15:53.720 --> 00:15:57.440
